      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Thyrs consume thermal energy. They have fire resistance 5, which stacks with one other source of fire resistance. Once per day as a reaction when a thyr takes fire damage, they can increase their fire resistance by 5 until the beginning of their next turn. Until the end of their next turn, all of the thyrâ€™s speeds increase by 30 feet, to a maximum of twice their normal speed using that form of movement. This increase counts as an enhancement bonus.</p>\n<p><em>System does not currently support stacked Energy Resistance bonuses. Emulate stacking by editing the modifier in the Modifier tab.</em></p>\n<p><em>Enable/Disable Reaction bonuses in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
